                     <interp inst="t18440610-1797-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 1 shawl, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440610-name-1409" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18440610-name-1409" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
